window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Blue and his Companions have solidified their positions, and are ready to head out into the world. They have new allies, new infrastructure, new information, and most importantly, goals.<br> <br> House Anell is a thorn.<br> The mage-kings are a poison.<br> Depletion is an existential threat.<br> <br> It's time to deal with all of it.<br> <br> The conclusion of Blue Core.</p>"; 
